	('OrbitsEdge', NULL, 'https://orbitsedge.com/', NULL, 'Infrastructure', NULL, 'GoDaddy Builder', 'React, RequireJS', NULL, NULL, 'OrbitsEdge proprietary SatFrame empowers space commercialization through a software-defined data infrastructure that delivers the agility to dynamically adapt to new demands. By leveraging an in-orbit virtualized architecture, ObitsEdge delivers high-performance computing, analytics and AI as-a-service. Our unique satellite protects technology designed for Earth from the harshness of space and includes power, cooling, satellite to satellite communications, avionics and IoT integration.', NULL, 'United States', '2018', 'Seed', '$0.00', '1-10', 'https://www.linkedin.com/company/orbitsedge/, https://twitter.com/OrbitsEdge', 'President: Sylvia France', 'orbitsedge.com', NULL, 'Not started', NULL, NULL, '5ee6861febf1ac9f5d6d49db_orbitsedge.png (https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3/u/37/37/1737604800000/BarZRd_0WsTwNWr0X55VjQ/UwcEDXOOICpf21niRhWp9H98d3fZwwk_6amfVKsyyHhPhtoreAwd7srSRwEwvSVz0vVqoUU1fjgjwwobsYnS3CT0FjlfjDYY44godovl_WNZENO3SWmPV9FPyoqNnwLwuhMyUQBf_3wkasiFFlxmkw/qs_z0h6cIImUROmlV5aMALKXVIxlVGFjycc03AP7N6s)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
